# <emoji> <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Body (wrap at 72): explain WHY, not what (the diff shows what).
#
# Refs: #123, fixes #456
#
# ── Gitmoji cheatsheet ─────────────────────────────────
# ✨ :sparkles:           new feature
# 🐛 :bug:                bug fix
# 📝 :memo:               docs
# ♻️  :recycle:            refactor
# 🔧 :wrench:             config
# 🚀 :rocket:             deploy / release
# ⚡ :zap:                perf
# ✅ :white_check_mark:   tests
# 🔥 :fire:               remove code
# 🔖 :bookmark:           release/tag
# 🚧 :construction:       WIP
# 💥 :boom:               breaking change
# 🔒 :lock:               security
# 🩹 :adhesive_bandage:   minor non-critical fix
# ── Full list: https://gitmoji.dev ─────────────────────
